      <title>丹麦央行称部分银行面临二氧化碳税风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/some-danish-lenders-face-risks-from-co2-tax-central-bank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥本哈根央行表示，丹麦对农业排放征税的计划将导致该国部分金融机构的减值费用上升，但不会威胁金融稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/some-danish-lenders-face-risks-from-co2-tax-central-bank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 08:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Banco BPM 将讨论 UniCredit 的 110 亿美元收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/banco-bpm-set-to-discuss-unicredit-s-11-billion-takeover-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Banco BPM SpA 将讨论 UniCredit SpA 的意外收购要约，投资者正在等待该银行对此举的回应，该举动震动了金融市场和罗马政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/banco-bpm-set-to-discuss-unicredit-s-11-billion-takeover-bid</guid>
